--[ 0x00 How to use

This is used with httplib2[1], which help locate CA certification files.


    import ca_certs_locater
    ca_certs_locater.get = lambda : '/path/to/cacerts.txt'

    import httplib2
    # ...


[1]: https://github.com/jcgregorio/httplib2

